snippet: Police Commissioner Raymond W. Kelly said the attacker had tried to rob the victim, and he stabbed her when she resisted.
abstract: Woman is stabbed on Manhattan’s Upper East Side during an alleged robbery attempt; unidentified victim is in stable condition, and police say they have detained a suspect.
lead_paragraph: Police Commissioner Raymond W. Kelly said the attacker had tried to rob the victim, and he stabbed her when she resisted.
